title: 287. Andy & DJ CTI: Dave Chappelle Attacked On Stage, Roe V. Wade & CDC Cellphone Data Tracking
itunes:title: 287. Andy & DJ CTI: Dave Chappelle Attacked On Stage, Roe V. Wade & CDC Cellphone Data Tracking
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ discuss Dave Chappelle being attacked onstage by an audience member while performing at Hollywood Bowl in Los Angeles, the Supreme Court's decision to overturn Roe v. Wade that provided women with a constitutional right to abortion, and the report that showed the CDC bought cellphone data to track vaccination & lockdown compliance.
